                d^2&=30^2+20^2-2(30)(20)\fe{\cos}{\theta}
                d^2&=1300-1200\fe{\cos}{\theta}
                \lzoo{t}{d^2}&=\lzoo{t}{1300-1200\fe{\cos}{\theta}}
                2d\lz{d}{t}&=1200\fe{\sin}{\theta}\lz{\theta}{t}
